fit and function. Experienced general contractors or <a href=\"https:\/\/sweeten.com\/advice-and-faq\/truth-design-build-firms\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">design-build firms<\/a> typically have millworkers they resource to create the kitchen to your specifications.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t<section class=\"elementor-section elementor-top-section elementor-element elementor-element-7a41def elementor-section-boxed elementor-section-height-default elementor-section-height-default\" data-id=\"7a41def\" data-element_type=\"section\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-container elementor-column-gap-default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-row\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column elementor-col-100 elementor-top-column elementor-element elementor-element-efc19da\" data-id=\"efc19da\" data-element_type=\"column\">\n\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-column-wrap elementor-element-populated\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-wrap\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-18d0fb1 elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"18d0fb1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-image\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"1000\" height=\"667\" src=\"https:\/\/sweeten.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/113569_Dan_Apt_010.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-image-53984\" alt=\"Galley kitchen leading out to dining area\" srcset=\"https:\/\/sweeten.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/113569_Dan_Apt_010.jpg 1000w, https:\/\/sweeten.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/113569_Dan_Apt_010-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/sweeten.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/02\/113569_Dan_Apt_010-600x400.jpg 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100v